column2: Unknown origin, myRT blog, Majlis Daerah Pekan, Majlis Daerah Rompin

Users to exercise discretion when using the dataset. Tioman Island is not necessarily part of Majlis Daerah Rompin, it is under Lembaga Pembangunan Tioman (TDA). TDA Boundaries could not be determined. The islands offshore of Rompin district could either belong to Rompin District or TDA.  While every effort has been undertaken to ensure the accuracy, we are not responsible for errors and omission that are arising from the dataset.
